"from G4633 (σκηνή);","strongs_def":"a hut or temporary residence, i.e. (figuratively) the human body (as the abode of the spirit)","kjv_def":"tabernacle"},"G4671":{"id":"G4671","lemma":"σοί","translit":"soí","derivation":"dative case of G4771 (σύ);","strongs_def":"to thee","kjv_def":"thee, thine own, thou, thy","pos":"pronoun","usage":"thee(200x), thou(14x), thy(4x)"},"G4609":{"id":"G4609","lemma":"Σίλας","translit":"Sílas","derivation":"contraction for G4610 (Σιλουανός);","strongs_def":"Silas, a Christian","kjv_def":"Silas","pos":"proper masculine noun","usage":"Silas(13x)"},"G4621":{"id":"G4621","lemma":"σῖτος","translit":"sîtos","derivation":"of uncertain derivation;","strongs_def":"grain, especially wheat","kjv_def":"corn, wheat","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"wheat(12x), corn(2x)"},"G4683":{"id":"G4683","lemma":"σπαργανόω","translit":"sparganóō","derivation":"from (a strip;","strongs_def":"from a derivative of the base of G4682 (σπαράσσω) meaning to strap or wrap with strips); to swathe (an infant after the Oriental custom)","kjv_def":"wrap in swaddling clothes","pos":"verb"},"G4650":{"id":"G4650","lemma":"σκορπίζω","translit":"skorpízō","derivation":"apparently from the same as G4651 (σκορπίος) (through the idea of penetrating);","strongs_def":"to dissipate, i.e. (figuratively) put to flight, waste, be liberal","kjv_def":"disperse abroad, scatter (abroad)","pos":"verb","usage":"scatter(3x)"},"G4618":{"id":"G4618","lemma":"σιτευτός","translit":"siteutós","derivation":"from a derivative of G4621 (σῖτος);","strongs_def":"grain-fed, i.e. fattened","kjv_def":"fatted","pos":"adjective","usage":"fatted(3x)"},"G4647":{"id":"G4647","lemma":"σκόλοψ","translit":"skólops","derivation":"perhaps from the base of G4628 (σκέλος) and G3700 (ὀπτάνομαι);","strongs_def":"withered at the front, i.e. a point or prickle (figuratively, a bodily annoyance or disability)","kjv_def":"thorn"},"G4674":{"id":"G4674","lemma":"σός","translit":"sós","derivation":"from G4771 (σύ);","strongs_